{"tid":419595,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"閩 粵 人 不 等 於 漢 人","createTime":"2017-09-30T15:30:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T02:04:15.000Z","uid":35790,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"317af9d2a3a7a1ece74ae47cd016e79874e222a6","tid":419595,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T15:30:33.000Z","msg":"&lt;轉PTT&gt;<br />\n閩粵人不等於漢人 <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/7ErazO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7ErazO5.jpg&h=89db5eeb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/3OKzY1H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3OKzY1H.jpg&h=0521dc19&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/jkA3X71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjkA3X71.jpg&h=974e9ea3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n林媽利教授的馬偕團隊根據台灣人的血緣做出研究，發現多數&quot;台灣人&quot;其實是平埔族與閩 粵移民的混血，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而閩粵移民其實是漢化的越人，並非我們一直以為的&quot;中原漢人&quot;。</span></span> 這套說法並沒有寫入教科書中，所以多數人仍以為，閩粵移民也是漢人，所以也應該是中 國人，而不知道，閩粵人其實早就拋棄了自己的越人文化，被漢文化同化。 可悲的是，平埔人也以為自己是漢人，然後高山族以為漢化的平埔是閩人，然後一併厭惡 之。這就表現在高山原民寧願把票給國民黨，而不願給本土、操閩南語(=漢化平埔)的民 進黨。 在這樣的基礎上，台灣的母語運動追尋的是誰的母語？台灣人使用的漢語文應該怎樣定位 ，都是個值得深思的問題。 但台灣人絕對不是純粹的漢人。而台灣人是不是中國人，就要看你覺得中國人的定義是什 麼了。 補~ 想深入了解就自己去翻這本書，我整理的內容有限，文本就在那裡，請自行檢視運用。 <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/UfYf1WY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUfYf1WY.jpg&h=5c42f1eb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/qSnQ38H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqSnQ38H.jpg&h=c40276fd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://bbstop.amassly.com/post/Gossiping_1LH8CpVu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbbstop.amassly.com%2Fpost%2FGossiping_1LH8CpVu&d=vu6s8LH4hirWXswi0N35yr5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=e55c9025\" target=\"_blank\">https://bbstop.amassly.com/post/Gossiping_1LH8CpVu</a>"},{"pid":"e3d45c62c8b00e74a4bb40a559bdf7683c4f1836","tid":419595,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T15:35:45.000Z","msg":"如果接受中原文化就係漢人<br />\n接受日本文化就係大和民族？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c15d1da98f39d5374d6dd27f23fe408ec89f4c","tid":419595,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T15:36:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果接受中原文化就係漢人<br />\n接受日本文化就係大和民族？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就好似接受美國文化就係美國人咁咋嘛,啱吖"},{"pid":"a9b7be54e8752c88d2f9b16704dbb57c615b1cbb","tid":419595,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T15:38:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果接受中原文化就係漢人<br />\n接受日本文化就係大和民族？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就好似接受美國文化就係美國人咁咋嘛,啱吖</blockquote><br />\n美國人唔係民族"},{"pid":"fe83bc97cc75c27068428730c568ce79f0d74645","tid":419595,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T15:38:49.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143d57ea2d0a1893bef463d14ad4c3181ac4a09f","tid":419595,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T15:52:56.000Z","msg":"閩粵人被屈做南漢人<br />\n鄭成功父係福建人 母係日本人<br />\n歷史書稱鄭成功做漢人<br />\n漢人統治台灣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36ef563b78c0937520ffba237e6c977cb048703","tid":419595,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1b85defec325b1a08be80a31e554321fdf3cc0","tid":419595,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:16:46.000Z","msg":"認祖歸宗 我地唔係支那漢族"},{"pid":"7b7a19841f65eac8c8b0a7f8de51a0910d193c73","tid":419595,"uid":35790,"lik